Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.88,0:00:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.58,0:01:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFFFF\blur3\bord0\fsp\fn方正楷体_GBK\b\fscx\fs62\pos(640,479.095)}『迷惘與頓悟』
